ehanae''\n***[[White-bellied moss mouse]], ''Pseudohydromys sandrae''\n**Genus ''[[Xeromys]]'' (False Water Rat)\n***[[False water rat]], ''Xeromys myoides''\n*''incertae sedis''\n**Genus ''[[Hyorhinomys]]''\n***''[[Hyorhinomys stuempkei]]''\n**Genus ''[[Mirzamys]]''\n***[[Mirza's western moss rat]], ''Mirzamys louiseae''\n***[[Mirza's eastern moss rat]], ''Mirzamys norahae''\n**Genus ''[[Musseromys]]''\n***[[Banahaw tree mouse]], ''Musseromys gulantang''\n***''[[Musseromys anacuao]]''\n***''[[Musseromys beneficus]]''\n***''[[Musseromys inopitatus]]''\n**Genus ''[[Paucidentomys]]''\n***''[[Paucidentomys vermidax]]''\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==References==\n*{{cite journal |ref=harv |bibcode=1993PNAS...90.3433C |jstor=2361758 |title=Molecular Evidence that the Spiny Mouse (Acomys) is More Closely Related to Gerbils (Gerbillinae) Than to True Mice (Murinae) |journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America |volume=90 |issue=8 |pages=3433\u20136 |last1=Chevret |first1=Pascale |last2=Denys |first2=Christiane |last3=Jaeger |first3=Jean-Jacques |last4=Michaux |first4=Jacques |last5=Catzeflis |first5=Francois M. |year=1993 |doi=10.1073/pnas.90.8.3433 |pmid=8475093 |pmc=46314 }}\n*{{cite journal |ref=harv |doi=10.3158/2158-5520-2.1.1 |title=Chapter 1: Seven New Species and a New Subgenus of Forest Mice (Rodentia: Muridae: Apomys) from Luzon Island |journal=Fieldiana Life and Earth Sciences |volume=2 |issue=2 |pages=1\u201360 |year=2011 |last1=Heaney |first1=Lawrence R. |last2=Balete |first2=Danilo S. |last3=Rickart |first3=Eric A. |last4=Alviola |first4=Phillip A. |last5=Duya |first5=Mariano Roy M. |last6=Duya |first6=Melizar V. |last7=Veluz |first7=M. Josefa |last8=Vandevrede |first8=Lawren |last9=Steppan |first9=Scott J.  }}\n*{{cite book |last1=Jacobs |first1=Louis L. |year=1978 |title=Fossil Rodents (Rhizomyidae & Muridae): From Neogene Siwalik Deposits, Pakistan |series=Bulletin of the Museum of Northern Arizona, 52 |oclc=4611